when you were in junior high.

00:10:34.509 --> 00:10:36.469 position:50% align:center
You still write in it.

00:10:36.553 --> 00:10:38.179 position:50% align:center
[NENE]
Dear, Sweet Teru,

00:10:38.263 --> 00:10:40.306 position:50% align:center
you did such a great job
addressing the school today

00:10:40.390 --> 00:10:41.641 position:50% align:center
