00:10:41.725 --> 00:10:44.477 position:50% align:center
And I can't even get into
how hot you looked!

00:10:44.561 --> 00:10:46.354 position:50% align:center
But don't forget that we're
keeping our relationship

00:10:46.438 --> 00:10:47.856 position:50% align:center
secret for now.

00:10:47.939 --> 00:10:49.315 position:50% align:center
